name: Kneeler Bushing
description: A hollow cylindrical bushing for church pew kneeler frames. The collared insert design features a wider collar (16.2mm OD) that seats against the outer face of the frame, and a narrower insert (13.1mm OD, 19mm tall) that presses into the frame hole. A 9.5mm bore passes through the center for hardware.

printSettings.bushing: Polymaker PLA Pro (Black) | 4 Wall Loops | 35% Gyroid Infill

assemblyGuide: Clean the frame hole, removing any debris or remnants of the old bushing.
Orient the bushing so the collar faces the outer surface of the frame.
Press the insert into the frame hole until the collar seats flush against the frame.
